---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Projecten | SASA" bodyClass="bg-surface text-on-surface font-body selection:bg-primary-container selection:text-on-primary-container">
<main>
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative pt-24 pb-16 px-6 overflow-hidden">
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
<span class="text-primary font-bold tracking-widest text-xs uppercase mb-4 block px-el" data-depth="0.9">ONS PORTFOLIO</span>
<h1 class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-secondary tracking-tight mb-8 px-el" data-depth="0.5">
  Onze <span class="text-primary">visie</span> in beeld
</h1>
<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed px-el" data-depth="0.3">
  Bij SASA geloven we in de synergie tussen digitale precisie en organische groei. Ontdek de transformatieverhalen die we samen met onze partners hebben gebouwd.
</p>
</div>
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-primary-container/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/4 w-64 h-64 bg-secondary-container/30 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
</section>
<!-- Bento Grid Section -->
<section class="py-16 px-6">
<div class="max-w-[90rem] mx-auto">
<div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12 items-start">
<!-- Left Column -->
<div class="lg:w-1/4 space-y-10 px-el" data-depth="0.6">
<div>
<span class="text-primary font-bold tracking-widest text-xs uppercase mb-2 block">ONS WERK</span>
<h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-extrabold text-secondary mb-6 leading-tight">Digitale ecosystemen bouwen</h2>
<div class="space-y-6 text-base text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed font-body">
<p>Elk project begint met een diepgaande verkenning van de essentie van het merk. We cultiveren digitale omgevingen waar bedrijven floreren en zich aanpassen aan het moderne web.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="bg-primary/10 p-8 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-primary/20 shadow-sm">
<div class="mb-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">auto_awesome</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-3">Duurzame innovatie</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
  Onze methodologie integreert toekomstgerichte technologieën met toegankelijke ontwerpprincipes voor langdurige relevantie.
</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Right Column: Image Grid -->
<div class="lg:w-3/4 w-full">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 h-auto md:h-[650px]">
<!-- Main Card -->
<div class="md:col-span-7 relative group overflow-hidden rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-2xl px-el" data-depth="0.35">
<img alt="Modern werkruimte" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" src="https://placehold.co/900x650"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-secondary/80 via-secondary/20 to-transparent"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-10 left-10 text-white">
<h3 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-2">Innovation Hub</h3>
<p class="text-lg opacity-90">Waar ideeën werkelijkheid worden</p>
</div>
<div class="absolute top-8 right-8">
<a href="/contact" class="bg-primary text-secondary px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold flex items-center gap-2 shadow-xl hover:bg-primary-fixed transition-all">
  Start jouw project
  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Right Grid -->
<div class="md:col-span-5 flex flex-col gap-6">
<div class="relative group flex-1 overflow-hidden rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-xl">
<img alt="Code op scherm" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" src="https://placehold.co/600x400"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-secondary/70 to-transparent"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-8 left-8 text-white">
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Robuuste architectuur</h3>
</div>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 h-48">
<div class="relative group overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] shadow-xl">
<img alt="Designteam" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" src="https://placehold.co/300x200"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-secondary/40 to-transparent"></div>
</div>
<div class="relative group overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] bg-secondary p-8 flex flex-col justify-center text-white shadow-xl border-b-4 border-primary">
<h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-primary mb-1">150+</h3>
<p class="opacity-70 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Succesvolle projecten</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Testimonials -->
<section class="bg-white py-24 px-6 overflow-visible">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-16">
<div>
<span class="text-primary font-bold tracking-widest text-xs uppercase mb-2 block">REFERENTIES</span>
<h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-extrabold text-secondary">Klanten aan het woord</h2>
</div>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mt-20">
<!-- Testimonial 1 -->
<div class="relative bg-surface-container-low p-10 md:p-14 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border border-white/50 pt-24 px-el" data-depth="0.45">
<div class="absolute -top-20 left-10 w-40 h-40 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border-4 border-white rotate-3 group hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500">
<img alt="Sarah Janssen" class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://placehold.co/160x160"/>
</div>
<div class="space-y-6">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container text-6xl opacity-30">format_quote</span>
<blockquote class="font-headline text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary leading-snug italic">
  "Het strategisch inzicht dat SASA meebracht naar ons project was transformatief. Ze herontwierpen niet alleen onze site; ze herdefinieerden onze digitale toekomst."
</blockquote>
<div class="pt-6 border-t border-outline-variant/30">
<p class="font-bold text-lg text-secondary">Sarah Janssen</p>
<p class="text-primary text-sm font-semibold">CEO bij Lumina Global</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Testimonial 2 -->
<div class="relative bg-primary p-10 md:p-14 rounded-3xl shadow-[0_30px_60px_rgba(123,211,69,0.25)] pt-24 mt-20 md:mt-0 border-b-4 border-on-primary-fixed-variant/20 px-el" data-depth="0.6">
<div class="absolute -top-20 right-10 w-40 h-40 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border-4 border-white -rotate-3 group hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500">
<img alt="Marc Dubois" class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://placehold.co/160x160"/>
</div>
<div class="space-y-6">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-primary-fixed text-6xl opacity-20">format_quote</span>
<blockquote class="font-headline text-2xl font-semibold text-on-primary-fixed leading-snug italic">
  "Samenwerken met SASA voelde als het toevoegen van een elite innovatielab aan ons team. Hun toekomstgerichte aanpak voor UI was precies wat onze startup nodig had."
</blockquote>
<div class="pt-6 border-t border-on-primary-fixed-variant/20">
<p class="font-bold text-lg text-on-primary-fixed">Marc Dubois</p>
<p class="text-on-primary-fixed-variant text-sm font-bold">Oprichter van NexaStream</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- CTA Section -->
<section class="px-6 py-24">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div class="bg-primary rounded-[2rem] relative overflow-hidden shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(123,211,69,0.3)] border-b-8 border-r-8 border-on-primary-fixed-variant/10 p-10 md:p-12">
<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-white/10 to-transparent"></div>
<div class="absolute -right-20 -bottom-20 w-80 h-80 bg-white/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
<div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-12">
<div class="max-w-2xl text-center md:text-left">
<h2 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-on-primary-fixed mb-6 leading-tight">
  Klaar voor een digitale transformatie?
</h2>
<p class="text-on-primary-fixed-variant text-lg md:text-xl font-medium opacity-90 leading-relaxed">
  Zet vandaag nog de stap naar een toekomstbestendig digitaal ecosysteem. Ons team staat klaar om jouw visie tot leven te wekken.
</p>
</div>
<div class="flex-shrink-0">
<a href="/contact" class="bg-secondary text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 flex items-center gap-3">
  Start je project
  <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>
